      • findDatasetVersions

        java.util.Collection<T> findDatasetVersions(CleanableDataset dataset)
                                     throws java.io.IOException
        Find dataset versions for the dataset at Path. Dataset versions are subdirectories of the input Path representing a single manageable unit in the dataset. See DatasetCleaner for more information.
        Parameters:
        dataset - Path to directory containing all versions of a dataset.
        Returns:
        Collection of DatasetVersion for each dataset version found.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
